'''Alan John Forey''' (born 1933) is reader emeritus in history at the [[University of Durham]]<ref>[https://www.dur.ac.uk/university.calendar/volumei/emeritus_titles/ Emeritus Titles.] University of Durham. Retrieved 4 December 2016.</ref> and an authority on the history of the [[military order (monastic society)|military order]]s of the [[middle ages]].<ref>[https://dx.doi.org/10.1484/M.STMH-EB.3.2397 Alan Forey (1933).] Brepols Online. Retrieved 5 December 2016.</ref> In 1994, his work was collected and published in the [[Variorum Collected Studies]] series as ''Military Orders and Crusades''.<ref>[https://www.routledge.com/Military-Orders-and-Crusades/Forey/p/book/9780860783985 Military Orders and Crusades.] Routledge. Retrieved 4 December 2016.</ref>
